			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is perhaps one of the simplest quest ing the game once you have your CoV faction up.
<br />

<br />
Go to skyshrine and ask for the tools -> hand tools to the scout -> kill captain -> hand in the disk to the scout for the reward. The captain can be single pulled by a lv 60+ and is almost impossible to land anything on as a magician. (could be a melee range thing)
<br />

<br />
What is a bit annoying is that once you have done the quest you can't do it again right away and it takes a while for the scout to despawn and respawn again. If the scout looks like it is holding a small bag, someone has done the quest recently and you have to wait. Respawn is a bit long, 12 hours (if I remember correctly)
<br />

<br />
The robe is nice (even with the -8 to dex and agi), the bracer is nicer (and they are not lore, so you can have two) and the talisman is very-very nice. Robe of haunted dreams is however a better robe, but it cost pp.
<br />

<br />
nmee<br />_________________<br /><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=407265">Nmee Lightarch</A>
<br />
Prestidigitator
<br />
<A href="http://www.povartarewalliance.org/">Povar Tarew Alliance</A></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
