				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">/pet hold
<br />
Pet turns and comes to you.
<br />
Giant summons the pet to him.
<br />
You now have ~12 seconds to pull out a new pet before the mob can summon again.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">
